             Abu Dhabi set up a special
department to devise its fiscal and budget policy, al-Ittihad
said, citing a decision from the emirateâ€™s crown prince, Sheikh
Mohamed Bin Zayed Al-Nahyan.  
 Ahmed Mubarak al-Mazroui will chair the Abu Dhabi Fiscal
